---
title: BBQ Sausage Skewers with Cheesy Wedges and a Rocket Salad
description: If there's one thing that makes us happy, it's seeing families cooking together in the kitchen! This is a great one to get kids involved in … especially threading the sausage and veggie chunks onto the skewers, which is pretty fun (but pretty messy!). Just remember to share your cooking pictures on social media!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bbq-sausage-skewers-28642762-f027e137.jpg
